  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Tank Hunter game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957440/extras/88fbcc4f005298b48b542e049290290c.avif?t=1744899433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957440/extras_big/88fbcc4f005298b48b542e049290290c.avif?t=1744899433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a 3D shooting game that combines mild survival and clearance of meat pigeons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience by defeating enemies and learn skills after leveling up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources to purchase props.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes several exquisite shooting levels and terrain, with a top-down angle and a third person perspective</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many bosses with different styles waiting for your challenge in the game</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Tank Hunter game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957440/extras/88fbcc4f005298b48b542e049290290c.avif?t=1744899433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957440/extras_big/88fbcc4f005298b48b542e049290290c.avif?t=1744899433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a 3D shooting game that combines mild survival and clearance of meat pigeons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience by defeating enemies and learn skills after leveling up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources to purchase props.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes several exquisite shooting levels and terrain, with a top-down angle and a third person perspective</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many bosses with different styles waiting for your challenge in the game</p>",
